title: [Zandactyl's Armory]
[Zandactyl's Outfitting]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin hangs on one of the varnished ebonwood walls.  A vine-carved mahogany table and an oval-shaped speckled marble counter sit in opposite corners while a bronzed drake sculpture rests on a speckled black marble floor.
